reviewText: Love the Spurs! Nothing more need be said.

Its a great story line about an ABA team that survived in going over to the NBA. finally won their 1st NBA Championship with David Robinson the veteran and Tim Duncan the rookie. You have to see the video, i recommend it. I is history in the making!!!

awsome video that goes through the whole playoffs including some backstage stuff and footage of the Spurs finally winning an NBA Title!
every so sweet.
